                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390916-name-237" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390916-name-237" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390916-name-237" type="surname" value="BOURN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390916-name-237" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN BOURN</persName>
                  </hi>. I lodge at the Angel public-house, Kit's-end, South Mimms. On the 25th of August, I was in the taproom—the prisoner and a person named Garratt were there—I fell asleep—my hat was by my side, and two handkerchiefs were in it—I awoke in about a quarter of an hour—I missed my handkerchiefs, and the prisoner was gone to South Mimms—I went after him, and gave him in charge—the handkerchiefs were found on him-these are them.</p>
